    "name": "Debut Project: Cooking Café",
    "steam_appid": 3155560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whip up Like-worthy meals and get tons of fans at a stylish café!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/153372a46bfb14746751d38d8133f025.poster.avif?t=1734597885\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/153372a46bfb14746751d38d8133f025.webm?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/153372a46bfb14746751d38d8133f025.mp4?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Creative cooking in a cool café!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a new café employee, you'll be taking orders and completing challenges on your journey to create recipes which will take social media by storm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share pics of your cooking to get Likes and boost your café's rating.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See if your culinary creativity can earn a million followers for the café!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/c317fc5a0d293c89f5fdc966fccd7208.poster.avif?t=1734597885\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/c317fc5a0d293c89f5fdc966fccd7208.webm?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/c317fc5a0d293c89f5fdc966fccd7208.mp4?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・A new café employee's journey to fame!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a new café employee, you'll take on each day by taking orders from customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create recipes worthy of sharing online to get Likes, boost the café's rating, and maybe even get a million followers someday.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the café becomes more popular, big-name influencers will start to visit and you'll even find that you have your very own fans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's not just the story of the café but your success story too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/9d5a02127ad019ac16b13d59336efd48.poster.avif?t=1734597885\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/9d5a02127ad019ac16b13d59336efd48.webm?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/9d5a02127ad019ac16b13d59336efd48.mp4?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Cook to your heart's content choosing from 80 different menu items and 271 toppings!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy making pancakes, crepes, Hamburg steaks, cakes, omelets and more through 13 cooking minigames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ice cream swirls on sweetcorn? Painting cute pictures on pancakes with syrup? Unleash your imagination choosing from 271 toppings and create Like-worthy, photogenic dishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With 80 different dishes to create, you won't be bored in the café kitchen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/0e91e0ad7da276f629d9d67dac487fe5.poster.avif?t=1734597885\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/0e91e0ad7da276f629d9d67dac487fe5.webm?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/0e91e0ad7da276f629d9d67dac487fe5.mp4?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・Share your creations on in-game social media!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you get Likes and positive comments? See what your followers think about your cooking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get more Likes to raise your Flavor Rank, allowing you to expand the café's menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete hashtag challenges or try your hand at making your very own special dishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reaching certain follower milestones will allow the café to expand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the café grow from small shop into a stylish, multi-floored influencer magnet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/10cca78aa6e3d244082a3be045ef2d1f.poster.avif?t=1734597885\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/10cca78aa6e3d244082a3be045ef2d1f.webm?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155560/extras/10cca78aa6e3d244082a3be045ef2d1f.mp4?t=1734597885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
